### ============================================
### HEALTH & SMOKE TESTS
### ============================================
### Quick verification tests to ensure the API is running properly
### Run these first before executing any other test suites
### 
### Endpoints Tested:
### - GET  /health      - Health check endpoint
### - GET  /            - API status and welcome message
### 
### Expected Results:
### - All endpoints should return 200 OK
### - Health check should confirm service status
### - Invalid endpoints should return 404
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost
@port = 80

### === SMOKE TESTS ===
### Run these first to verify the API is operational

### Test 1: Health Check
# Verify the API server is running and healthy
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{port}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Test 2: API Status & Welcome Message
# Get the API welcome message and basic info
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{port}}/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### === ERROR HANDLING TESTS ===

### Test 3: Invalid Endpoint (Should Return 404)
# Verify proper error handling for non-existent routes
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{port}}/invalid-endpoint
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Test 4: Invalid HTTP Method (Should Return 404/405)
# Test unsupported HTTP method on valid endpoint
DELETE {{baseUrl}}:{{port}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### === EXPECTED RESPONSES ===
###
### Test 1 - Health Check:
### {
###   "status": "healthy",
###   "timestamp": "2025-10-07T12:00:00.000Z",
