### ============================================
### TROUBLESHOOTING
### ============================================
###
### If tests fail:
### 1. Verify server is running: npm start
### 2. Check port 80 is accessible (may need admin/sudo)
### 3. Verify no firewall blocking localhost:80
### 4. Check console for server startup errors
### 5. Verify all environment variables are set
###
